{"id":"quiz9","titre":"Compositions et Second degré","questions":[{"id":"q1","type":"qcm","enonce":"Quelle est la dérivée de f(x) = (ax + b)^n ?","options":["n(ax+b)^{n-1}","an(ax+b)^{n-1}","ax^{n-1}","n(ax+b)^n"],"correctIndex":1},{"id":"q2","type":"vrai_faux","enonce":"La dérivée de la fonction racine de u est u' / (2 * racine de u).","reponse":true},{"id":"q3","type":"trous","enonce":"La dérivée de f(x) = (3x + 1)² est f'(x) = {{1}}.","reponsesAttendues":["6(3x+1) / 18x+6"]},{"id":"q4","type":"relier","question":"Associe la dérivée.","pairs":[{"left":"cos(ax+b)","right":"-a*sin(ax+b)"},{"left":"sin(ax+b)","right":"a*cos(ax+b)"},{"left":"u(ax+b)","right":"a*u'(ax+b)"}]},{"id":"q5","type":"qcm","enonce":"Quelle est la dérivée de f(x) = (x² + 1)³ ?","options":["3(x²+1)²","6x(x²+1)²","2x(x²+1)","3x²"],"correctIndex":1}]}